; Test value exchange with --exchange
; Covers value.cc (value exchange with commodity conversion)

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/01/01 GBP $1.30

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    100 EUR
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Test
    Expenses:Travel    50 GBP
    Assets:Cash

test bal --exchange '$' Expenses
             $175.00  Expenses
             $110.00    Food
              $65.00    Travel
--------------------
             $175.00
end test
